column1: There wasn't anything in this world.
There wasn't anything to see in this world.
There was much to see in this world.
There wasn't much of a world.
There we stood against the world.
There we rode against the world.
There we were standing in the world.
There I said I hadn't seen the world.
There I stood thinking about the world.
There won't really be anyone left in this world.
There won't really be too much in this world.
There won't really be anyone left to see the world.
There won't be anyone left in the world.
There wasn't much left in the world.
There wasn't anything left in the world.
There was something left in the world.
There wasn't anything left in this world.
There won't be anyone here in the world.
